# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ShareGrid — Root env notice
#
# There are NO env vars at the root level.
# Environment variables live in each sub-project:
#
#   backend/.env    ← copy from backend/.env.example  (DO NOT commit this file)
#   frontend/.env   ← copy from frontend/.env.example (if needed)
#
# Quick start:
#   cp backend/.env.example backend/.env
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
